Note on source material:

The persona, place, piece, position, and process files in this folder are original works by Kai Schlüter.
They are built from the operating logic of 198 cultures across 5 regions but do not reproduce those cultures.
No intellectual property in any of the national cultures, historical events, symbols, or identities
drawn on is claimed. The KAI HACKS AI architecture — its methods, templates, and structural
elements — is the original contribution claimed under this license.

